    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/8d3388346893f7e9fb30848f6ce9b763.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/8d3388346893f7e9fb30848f6ce9b763.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/8d3388346893f7e9fb30848f6ce9b763.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>《Tales of the Forgotten》是一款第一人称步行模拟恐怖游戏，采用PSX风格的画面。体验三段关于幽灵的短篇故事，它们出没于日常场所。惊吓与诡异瞬间潜伏在每个角落。每个故事都有多个结局等待解锁。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏总时长约为45-60分钟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事1：镜花水月</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/dbfd0b1bf78f5a3c93587e9b116ac2ce.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/dbfd0b1bf78f5a3c93587e9b116ac2ce.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/dbfd0b1bf78f5a3c93587e9b116ac2ce.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你刚买了第一套房子，迫不及待地想搬进去。但一个不速之客正将你的梦想之家变成一场噩梦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/d03d6e9adbb84341deb4db04cf2aa747.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/d03d6e9adbb84341deb4db04cf2aa747.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/d03d6e9adbb84341deb4db04cf2aa747.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事2：洗衣夜</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/70e218a1876a1d62f0fbd03885dd9dad.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/70e218a1876a1d62f0fbd03885dd9dad.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/70e218a1876a1d62f0fbd03885dd9dad.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>深夜，你独自一人在自助洗衣店洗衣服。至少，你是这么认为的，直到你突然意识到一个幽灵正在向你求助。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/9d942cb93983cc52522369c1a29e0287.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/9d942cb93983cc52522369c1a29e0287.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/9d942cb93983cc52522369c1a29e0287.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事3：未完成的事务</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/4e3319c48df8b2eef00103931394087d.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/4e3319c48df8b2eef00103931394087d.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/4e3319c48df8b2eef00103931394087d.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在夜班时担任清洁工，工作地点是一个看似空荡荡的销售办公室。随着夜晚的深入，你逐渐发现多名幽灵已经与你共处一室。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/cd8dfdf00e27e8a03d89661c3a30a5c7.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/cd8dfdf00e27e8a03d89661c3a30a5c7.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/cd8dfdf00e27e8a03d89661c3a30a5c7.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多重结局</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/3c9d0a991960f1c80f45eeb3d19bd0ef.poster.avif?t=1771880714\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/3c9d0a991960f1c80f45eeb3d19bd0ef.webm?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157310/extras/3c9d0a991960f1c80f45eeb3d19bd0ef.mp4?t=1771880714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个故事都有多个结局可供探索和解锁。</p>",
